metadata.name: 8 seconds
metadata.description:
County Fair - AI Nostalgia captures the feeling of being at a Midwest country fair as a child in the 1980s, with its mix of fun and joy, weirdness and incredibility.

I intentionally kept post-prompt editing to a minimum to allow the strangeness and quirks of AI to come through, providing a historical look at what MidJourney was like during this particular time with these specific circumstances.

At the county fair, children often saw things that were nearly unbelievable, so the weirdness and wonder that shows up in these pieces strangely matches my childhood perception.
